sentences: In 2014 he made his first appearance at the iconic V-festival.
Following this, in 2016 he went on to make his debut at Disclosure & Rudimental’s new Wildlife festival.
In December 2012, TS7 signed to the talent management company 2-Tone Entertainment and shortly afterwards to Liverpool-based dance music label 3Beat Records/Universal Records.
The single was released on 17 February 2013 and went on to become a DJ favourite.
In 18 July 2013, TS7 joined the UK’s Kiss FM.
In 19 February 2015, as KissFresh, Kiss’s spinoff station, had a relaunch, TS7 was given a Saturday night slot from 11.00pm to midnight.
TS7 is also a DJ on Kiss FM and Kiss Fresh where he hosts a Thursday night show.
He was introduced to DJing and garage music at an early age and began to play in local nightclubs within the garage and bassline club scene.
Producing started at the young age of 14, when he managed to get hold of the software ‘Fruityloops’ (now known as FL Studio).
He first mixed from 7.00pm to 8.00pm every Saturday on the “Kiss Dance Weekend” block.
In 19 February 2015, as KissFresh, Kiss’s spinoff station, had a relaunch, TS7 was given a Saturday night slot from 11.00pm to midnight.
Later on, this slot was moved to Thursday nights, and still in use till today.
TS7 has also presented Kiss FM's DJ EZ show on Thursday night several times alongside fellow Kiss FM DJs Majestic and Mike Delinquent.
